  "prompt": "Which are the top software companies in Ahmedabad for .net developers?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, Ahmedabad has a growing tech ecosystem with several companies that hire .NET developers. Here are some of the prominent software companies in Ahmedabad known for their work in .NET development and related technologies:\n\n1. **Tachyon Technologies** - A software development company that specializes in web and mobile app development, often using .NET among other technologies.\n\n2. **Krish TechnoLabs** - Focuses on eCommerce solutions and custom software development, with strong capabilities in .NET technology.\n\n3. **MindIT** - Known for providing IT solutions including .NET development, they cater to various industries and help businesses with custom software applications.\n\n4. **Cimpress Technology India** - Part of the Cimpress family, this company works on a variety of software solutions, including those based on the .NET framework.\n\n5. **Aaseya IT Services** - Specializes in providing IT services and has a significant focus on .NET development as part of their offerings.\n\n6. **Techno Infonet** - A web and software development company that uses .NET framework in its project portfolio.\n\n7. **Aalap Technologies** - Known for providing custom software development services including .NET solutions, primarily serving SMEs.\n\n8. **Think360** - Offers a range of software solutions with a focus on .NET applications for enterprise needs.\n\n9. **Sparx IT Solutions** - A global IT service provider that employs .NET technologies in various projects, focusing on custom solutions.\n\n10. **Gadgeon Smart Systems** - Though they have a diverse tech stack, Gadgeon works with .NET technologies for certain projects, focusing on smart solutions and IoT.\n\nThese companies are known for their innovative work and typically look for skilled .NET developers to enhance their teams. Job seekers interested in .NET development in Ahmedabad would benefit from looking into these firms, as well as exploring local job boards and networking opportunities in the tech community.",
